    <item>
      <title>高盛所罗门预计 IPO 活动将会回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-13/goldman-s-solomon-expects-ipo-activity-to-pick-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛董事长兼首席执行官戴维·所罗门 (David Solomon) 表示，他担心上市公司数量减少，但预计 IPO 活动将在 2024 年下半年在法国凡尔赛举行的“选择法国”峰会上有所回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-13/goldman-s-solomon-expects-ipo-activity-to-pick-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 15:10:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛所罗门认为法国在支持商业方面取得了更多进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/goldman-s-solomon-sees-france-making-more-pro-business-strides</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大卫·所罗门表示，随着高盛集团近年来将其巴黎员工数量增加了两倍，法国领导人为使该国对企业更加友好而做出的努力让他深受鼓舞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/goldman-s-solomon-sees-france-making-more-pro-business-strides</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 15:06:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦称中国在贸易问题上不“按规则行事”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-13/yellen-says-china-isn-t-playing-by-the-rules-on-trade-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在接受彭博电视台采访时表示，她希望中国不会对华盛顿为保护其投资而采取的任何措施进行“重大”报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-13/yellen-says-china-isn-t-playing-by-the-rules-on-trade-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 15:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
